{"word":"Rehob","slug":"rehob","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Rehob</b> <a href=\"#/H7340\">H7340</a> <br/> 1. Father of Hadadezer, king of Zobah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=8&verse=3'>2Sa 8:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=8&verse=12'>2Sa 8:12</a><br/> 2. A Levite who sealed the covenant with Nehemiah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=10&verse=11'>Neh 10:11</a><br/> 3. A town in northern Palestine:<br/> - The limit of the investigation made by the twelve spies<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=13&verse=21'>Num 13:21</a> <br/> - Possessed by the Syrians<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=10&verse=6'>2Sa 10:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=10&verse=8'>2Sa 10:8</a> <br/> - Called Beth-Rehob<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=10&verse=6'>2Sa 10:6</a> <br/> 4. An unlocated town of Asher<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=19&verse=28'>Jos 19:28</a><br/> 5. A Levitical city of Asher<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=19&verse=30'>Jos 19:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=21&verse=31'>Jos 21:31</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=6&verse=75'>1Ch 6:75</a><br/> Canaanites not driven from<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=1&verse=31'>Jdg 1:31</a>"}]}